# AIM Specialization in JavaScript - Blackjack Game
Built by: Taj-Hakeem Ryles

## Project Description
This is a browser based Blackjack card games built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.
It allows for multiple player and simulates a real Blackjack game play.
Some of the key features are:
    - Multiplayer support
    - Multi deck play
    - Shuffle deck 
    - Ace handling logic
    - Win/Lose conditions

## Tech Stack Used
- HTML & CSS : UI
- JavaScript : Game Logic
- Vitest : Testing
- Hosting : Netlify


The following **required** functionality is completed:

- [x] Dealing in correct order.
- [x] .5 to 1 second delay in dealing each card to see order if dealing is correct.
- [x] Game can play with multiple decks.
- [x] Reshuffle when 60-75 cards left.
- [x] One, two or three players plus dealer.
- [x] Dealer getting soft 17.
- [ ] Splitting
- [ ] Betting
- [ ] Doubling down

The following are **optional** features:

- [ ] Animate dealing and flipping of cards
- [ ] Animate shuffling of cards
- [ ] Adding sound effects
- [ ] Different looking deck of cards
- [ ] Choice of differently looking decks of cards to choose from (in f we can find some)
- [x] Demo of game play to go along with rules

The following **additional** features are implemented:

- [x] Implamented unit tests for some of the functions.
- [x] Active website : blkjck.xyz

